pageProduct.name: Scholl Gel Activ Insoles For Flat Shoes
pageProduct.description:
Information

Welcome to the world of Scholl GelActiv

Enjoy the comfort of GelActiv in your high heeled shoes. Make shoes more comfortable or give your beloved unwearables a second chance, with Scholl GelActiv Insoles.

Cushioning

Enjoy cushioning during every step of the day.

For All Women's Shoes

GelActiv Insoles come in different designs for all kinds of women's shoes.

Non-Slip Technology

Our Non-Slip Technology makes sure that your foot has a firm stand in the shoe.

Scholl GelActiv Technology

Discover the unique Scholl GelActiv Technology in our range of insoles, which improves the comfort of your shoes all day, for all kinds of shoes.

• Ultra-slim transparent design

• Relieves pressure for less-stressed feet

• Extra cushioning on ball of foot

• Does not crowd toes

• Ultra-slim transparent design

• Extra cushioning on ball of foot

• Does not crowd toes

• Ultra-slim transparent design

• Does not crowd toes

• Ultra-slim transparent design

• Relieves pressure forless-stressed feet

• Does not crowd toes

General Information

Scholl GelActiv Insoles for Flat Shoes offer all day comfort

Scholl GelActiv insoles offer extra comfort for flat shoes. Designed for narrow style flat shoes to provide extra cushioning and shock absorption under the heels for lighter feeling feet all day. Does not crowd toes. Stays firmly in place. Suitable for flat shoes and boots. Suitable for shoe sizes UK: 3-75, AUS: 4-8, EUR: 35-40.5

Suitable For: Flat shoes and boots

Size: 1 Pack

KEY FEATURES

• All day comfort
• Extra comfort for flat shoes
• Extra cushioning
• Shock absorption
• GelActiv material

Warnings

Discontinue use if you experience adverse reaction.

Directions

- Remove plastic backing.
- Look for marking to indicate left (L) versus right (R) insole.
- Place insole in show sticky side down and line up heel of insole within back of shoe.
- Replace after 6 months or first signs of wear.

Suitable for shoes sizes
UK: 3-7.5
EUR: 35-40.5
AUS: 4-8

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes

Recycling Code: 1 PET(E)| 21 PAP
